

在Mac 上面找到: id_rsa.pub

engchaoma@Pengchaos-MacBook-Pro ~ % cd .ssh
pengchaoma@Pengchaos-MacBook-Pro .ssh % ls
id_rsa		id_rsa.pub	known_hosts	known_hosts.old

pengchaoma@Pengchaos-MacBook-Pro .ssh % cat id_rsa.pub 
ssh-rsa  pengchaoma@Pengchaos-MacBook-Pro.local

在远程主机上 找到 authorized_keys

allen@ubuntu:~$ cd .ssh/
allen@ubuntu:~/.ssh$ ls
authorized_keys

编辑 authorized_keys
allen@ubuntu:~/.ssh$ vim authorized_keys

将Mac 的 id_rsa.pub 内容 copy 到 authorized_keys：

cat authorized_keys 
ssh-rsa  pengchaoma@Pengchaos-MacBook-Pro.local

即可设置完成！！

